hotocurrent as the nanoparticles-free device and\nreducing thus significantly the toxicity of the device. Providing the\nrequirements related to the size, shape, position, composition, and\nconcentration of nanoparticles for the PSCs photocurrent enhancement, our study\nestablishes guidelines for a future development of highly-efficient,\nenvironmentally friendly and low-cost plasmonic perovskite solar cells.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 May 2019 15:16:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
